{"id": 1633, "genre": 1000, "title": "【好奇心x智选假日酒店】即使你心很大，在住酒店的时候也会留意哪些安全细节？", "description": "啊！出门在外，我那风雨飘摇的安全感！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 20873, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170418131118v6p9GhAyB5Jb8Q3C.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-18T17:00:16Z", "questions": [{"id": 2165, "title": "【好奇心x智选假日酒店】即使你心很大，在住酒店的时候也会留意哪些安全细节？", "content": "【好奇心x智选假日】即使你心很大，你在住酒店的时候会留意哪些安全细节？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 193465, "content": "入住后如果会外泄个人隐私，拉黑", "image": "img/option/option/20170418015938xNv2kadHU7qAiS9E.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193466, "content": "检查电梯门禁卡，是否要刷卡才能到专门楼层", "image": "img/option/option/20170418015902yEeutKIGJHk7D3XV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193468, "content": "门缝里塞小卡片，一定差评", "image": "img/option/option/20170418015644wLoEnO0TPhHZkr6I.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193473, "content": "不会喝水壶烧的第一遍开水", "image": "img/option/option/20170418015409eU4v3uTH7oKw9sJP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193474, "content": "睡前会锁上别门器和防盗链", "image": "img/option/option/20170418015240SdFfAt1VryhQCIUk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193476, "content": "一般不会用提供的浴巾和毛巾，床单也会看看是不是够干净", "image": "img/option/option/20170418014722GeA7zlJtiqk5Nbop.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193477, "content": "将大堂设在非首层的其他楼层的酒店，一般比较靠谱", "image": "img/option/option/201704180144255ZGWVl2cw41CFN7S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193478, "content": "在意酒店隔音，隔音不好的酒店很难住啊", "image": "img/option/option/20170418013722vO3XISawyHW6KjZ8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 193479, "content": "餐厅的食物新鲜好吃不糊弄的话，会加分", "image": "img/option/option/20170418013538hYrUT3gQtBCWP4vy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}